rows.label: qst002309_msg0003
rows.name:
The one that was stolen
from me the other day...

rows.label: qst002309_msg0004
rows.name:
I see... So you were the culprits.
You've come to turn yourselves in.

rows.label: qst002309_msg0005
rows.name:
In the name of Marveni-sama,
I shall pass judgment.

rows.label: qst002309_msg0006
rows.name:
I see, you were asked by
a Nopon named Moruru.

rows.label: qst002309_msg0007
rows.name:
You know where he is, don't
you? Please take me to him.
